						<summary>

						<p>Slab built into the wall of the house of Nurul Hassan in Sultānwāḍi.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Sōmēśvara II 11th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>Records a gift of land to god Beṭṭadadēva by <hi rend="italic">paṭṭasāhaṇi</hi> Ādityarasa who is described as <hi rend="italic">kaṭṭidalagu</hi> of (Chālukya) Sōmēśvara [II]. It is in characters of the 11th century A.D.</p>						

